      • ACR_VALUES

        public static final String ACR_VALUES
        Parameter usage location: OpenID Connect authentication request parameter. Used to specify Authentication Context Class Reference (ACR) values. These represent requested Level of Assurance (LoA), which is similar in concept to AuthLevel, but is may be mapped to any auth type (auth level, auth chain, module, etc).
        See Also:
        3.1.2.1 Authentication Request, Constant Field Values
